{"title":"You can now rent ex-pro bikes from Cavendish, Terpstra and more in Flanders","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/flanders-classic-bike-rental","date":1705678456000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/flanders-classic-bike-rental\">You can now rent ex-pro bikes from Cavendish, Terpstra and more in Flanders</a></p>\n\n<p>The Flandrien Hotel has teamed up with Bike Rent Manager to offer what it says is the world’s first classic bike rental service. Based out of the cycling-centric hotel and holiday venue, riders can now rent ex-pro team bikes from the likes of QuickStep, Lotto Soudal and Team Sky, ridden by Mark Cavendish, Niki Terpstra, Mat Hayman and more, to take on the infamous cobbles just like their heroes (though perhaps a tad slower).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Flandrien Hotel also hosts a number of other classic bikes, including the first carbon bike to win the Tour de France, which <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/flandrien-hotel-classic-road-bikes\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Cyclist </em>went to visit firsthand back in 2021.</a></p>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/trek-madone-history\">The complete history of the Trek Madone</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/bike-history-giant-tcr\">The complete history of the Giant TCR</a>\r\n               