       </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div>\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"728\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_pinarello-970x728.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_pinarello-970x728.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_pinarello-300x225.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_pinarello-768x576.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_pinarello-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_pinarello-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_pinarello-750x563.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_pinarello-1140x855.jpg 1140w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>The partnership aims to allow everyone from hobbyists to cycling fanatics to ride the region’s famed routes on bikes that partook in the history itself. The rental collection includes Alejandro Valverde’s Pinarello Prince FPX, resplendent with Campagnolo Bora Ultra wheels and Record groupset.</p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"728\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_mathew_hayman-970x728.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_mathew_hayman-970x728.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_mathew_hayman-300x225.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_mathew_hayman-768x576.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_mathew_hayman-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_mathew_hayman-750x563.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_mathew_hayman-1140x855.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel_mathew_hayman.jpg 2000w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>You can also rent Mathew Hayman’s Colnago C-50 Extreme Power from his early days of racing and, if those don’t take your fancy, you can also choose from bikes ridden by Mark Cavendish, Caleb Ewan, Rigoberto Urán and many more.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"932\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel-1-970x932.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel-1-970x932.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel-1-300x288.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel-1-768x738.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel-1-750x720.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel-1-1140x1095.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/flandrien_hotel-1.jpg 1144w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The service includes options for recovery wagon mechanics and bike replacements as well as wheel upgrades to give the classic steeds a modern flourish. To find out more, go to <a href=\"https://flandrienhotel.com/\" target=\"_blank\">flandrienhotel.com</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/flanders-classic-bike-rental\">You can now rent ex-pro bikes from Cavendish, Terpstra and more in Flanders</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a>.</p>","author":"Charlotte Head &#124; Tech Writer","siteTitle":"Cyclist.co.uk","siteHash":"561486e7070fa5351de9318ad0fa26c2a39332acba5fc7c7d1694a01d53d431e","entryHash":"4000f07e4d384a93bff66e16924256a13f2e790b33f376c59d574e2be14edf4b","category":"Cycling"}